{"title":"黄土窑","authors":["白亮"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":1,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土窑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些长期和泥土亲近的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父老乡亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做梦都在土层里面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和所有的根系轻轻叙谈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以致他们自身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也成为朴素而坚韧的根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶尔进城一回"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身的土腥气抖也不抖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那气韵，弥漫成我们赖以生存的精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个在窑洞里住了十三年的湖南人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自如地挥动巨手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使一种思想成熟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并留下不少诗篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着门前的河水流传"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多年之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看到弓背的窑洞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地倾诉梦境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬暖夏凉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像父亲种出的粮食"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将力量传达给我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论在哪个季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土高原上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些永不失明的瞳孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会用深邃的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将我们坚定地向前推动"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}